## Quality Gates

### Coverage Thresholds

| Metric | Minimum |
|--------|---------|
| Line Coverage | ≥ {{ coverage_line }}% |
| Branch Coverage | ≥ {{ coverage_branch }}% |

### Test Categories

1. **Unit** — domain models, engines, business rules
2. **Integration** — database + framework
3. **API** — HTTP/gRPC/GraphQL endpoints
{%- if contract_tests == "True" %}
4. **Contract** — parametrized business rules
{%- endif %}
5. **E2E** — full flow with real database
{%- if performance_tests == "True" %}
6. **Performance** — latency SLAs, throughput, resource usage
{%- endif %}
{%- if smoke_tests == "True" %}
7. **Smoke** — black-box against running environment
{%- endif %}

### Test Naming

```
[methodUnderTest]_[scenario]_[expectedBehavior]
```

### Merge Checklist

- [ ] All tests passing
- [ ] Coverage ≥ {{ coverage_line }}% line, ≥ {{ coverage_branch }}% branch
- [ ] Zero compiler/linter warnings
- [ ] Security review for sensitive changes
